
We are creating a gym application which will prompt and ask the user what exactly is it that they're looking for  in the main screen (ie nutrition plan or workout plan). 
Once the user selects their desired option either a nutrition plan will be displayed based on their BMI or a screen asking which muscle groups workout are they looking for which further has 3 categories advanced , beginner and intermediate. 
Whichever one the user selects will be displayed. The user can also obtain a 7 day workout plan and also look up trainer information and their charges. 
The user will also be asked to rate the application and track their monthly progress based on their weight and their waist size.
